title: Punnitse ja Saasta
description: Oulu branch is back. Carries plenty of vegan items such as raw materials for lasagna, shampoos and other cosmetics, mayonnaise, chocolate bars, flapjacks, oils, teas, nuts, grains, falafel and many more. The only non-veg item in the store is biscuits with shrimp flavoring. Located in the center, on the opposite side of Kuudes Maku, very close to the sea.
